{"tid":843472,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【息魔嚇窒】沙田第一城3房減價72萬沽","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T07:54:44.000Z","uid":174649,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfc23f11b65a9243bd9d9a3aed693e73d56a1bb","tid":843472,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"本港銀行加息後，業主擴大議價空間，刺激成交。新界指標上車屋苑沙田第一城，加息後已錄最少3宗成交。中原地產侯惠良表示，近日受加息影響，業主願提供較大議價空間，其中24座中層B室，實用面積447方呎，3房間隔，開價780萬元，剛減價72萬至708萬元易手，呎價15,839元。新買家為用家，感單位價錢合預算而購入自住。原業主則於1991年以102萬元購入單位，持貨27年，是次沽貨獲利606萬元離場，單位升值約5.9倍。<br />\n屋苑加息後另一宗成交為50座低層A室，實用面積284方呎，叫價510萬元，減至508.8萬元沽出，呎價17,916元。另43座低層A室，實用面積284方呎，成交價502.5萬元，呎價17,694元，屬近期市價。<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538376464_4f94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538376464_4f94.jpg&h=cf1057b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7b94a44e61378a6bbe1df54beb8caa768a092a4","tid":843472,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:32:51.000Z","msg":"快撚啲樓爆！<br />\n大把後生仔等緊呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbfc8a266c2ef05f1f12b37e85ab041df0d0cf3","tid":843472,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d54a7e27def8615ebd863a98eea256ea68216bac","tid":843472,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"27年賺得6球算少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6130a61b0186c181739ca5b44e0bcaef4d7af208","tid":843472,"uid":115468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"1991年我都未出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}